we type that this daily email—yes, the one you are about to read and perhaps even
enjoy—now has 2 million subscribers. We always said: When the equivalent of the
population of Slovenia is reading our email, we know we’ve made it big time.

tspan.tspan: Well look at us now, ma! Thanks so much to everyone who helped us along our journey.
